ples\\n(ii) Non-Brahmin peasant proprietors\\n(iii) Jain institutions\\n(iv) Maintenance of a school\\n\\nCodes:","question_hi":"चोल अभिलेखों में भूमि के प्रकार (सूची-I) को लाभार्थी (सूची-II) के साथ सुमेलित कीजिए:\\n\\nसूची-I\\n(a) वेल्लानवगई\\n(b) शलभोग\\n(c) देवदान\\n(d) पल्लीच्चंदम\\n\\nसूची-II\\n(i) मंदिर\\n(ii) गैर-ब्राह्मण किसान मालिक\\n(iii) जैन संस्थान\\n(iv) स्कूल का रखरखाव\\n\\nकूट:","option_a":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(iv), (c)-(i), (d)-(iii)","option_b":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(i), (c)-(iv), (d)-(iii)","option_c":"(a)-(i), (b)-(iv), (c)-(ii), (d)-(iii)","option_d":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(iv), (c)-(i), (d)-(ii)","option_a_hi":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(iv), (c)-(i), (d)-(iii)","option_b_hi":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(i), (c)-(iv), (d)-(iii)","option_c_hi":"(a)-(i), (b)-(iv), (c)-(ii), (d)-(iii)","option_d_hi":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(iv), (c)-(i), (d)-(ii)"},{"id":595,"quiz_id":48,"topic_id":1010,"sort_order":10,"question":"In the Chola military organization, the highly trained and fiercely loyal royal bodyguards who swore to defend the king with their lives were known as:","question_hi":"चोल सैन्य संगठन में, उच्च प्रशिक्षित और अत्यंत वफादार शाही अंगरक्षक जो अपने जीवन के साथ राजा की रक्षा करने की शपथ लेते थे, उन्हें किस रूप में जाना जाता था?","option_a":"Kaikkolas","option_b":"Velaikkarar","option_c":"Senapatis","option_d":"Nattars","option_a_hi":"कैक्कोलस","option_b_hi":"वेलाईक्कारर","option_c_hi":"सेनापति","option_d_hi":"नाट्टार"},{"id":596,"quiz_id":48,"topic_id":1010,"sort_order":11,"question":"Arrange the following Chola rulers in chronological order of their reign:\\n\\n1. Rajendra I\\n2. Parantaka I\\n3. Kulothunga I\\n4. Rajaraja I\\n\\nSelect the correct code:","question_hi":"निम्नलिखित चोल शासकों को उनके शासनकाल के कालक्रमानुसार व्यवस्थित कीजिए:\\n\\n1. राजेन्द्र प्रथम\\n2. परान्तक प्रथम\\n3. कुलोत्तुंग प्रथम\\n4. राजराज प्रथम\\n\\nसही कूट का चयन कीजिए:","option_a":"2, 4, 1, 3","option_b":"2, 1, 4, 3","option_c":"4, 2, 1, 3","option_d":"4, 1, 2, 3","option_a_hi":"2, 4, 1, 3","option_b_hi":"2, 1, 4, 3